    "description": "<p>You may use an action and spend 5 Mind Points to perform an Opposed <strong>【INS + WLP】 </strong>Check against an enemy that can hear and understand you. If you succeed, that enemy loses <strong>【SL × 5】</strong> Mind Points, suffers a status effect of your choice between dazed and shaken, and all sources deal <strong>【SL】</strong> extra damage to them until the start of your next turn.</p><p>You gain a bonus equal to <strong>【SL】</strong> to your <strong>【INS + WLP】</strong> Checks for this Skill.</p><hr /><ul><li><p><strong>You Perform: </strong>@CHECK[ins wlp ($sl)]</p></li><li><p><strong>Target Loses</strong>: @LOSS[$sl*5 mp]</p></li><li><p><strong>Target Suffers:</strong> @EFFECT[dazed], or @EFFECT[shaken], and @EFFECT[Compendium.projectfu.skills.Item.E0u1uXks8xbdQ3Cb]{Effect: Condemn}</p></li></ul>",
